   3.991232245354739*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ef49ebdd-26f3-43be-8868-\
694947df3e94"],

Cell["\<\
It remains to check whether the model is 2-minimal. For this purpose, we \
apply Lemma 2.2 from the article by Br\[ODoubleDot]ker and Davies.\
\>", "Text",
